# Stock Price Prediction using Machine Learning

## Overview
This project aims to predict stock closing prices using historical data and basic machine learning techniques.

## Dataset
- Source: Yahoo Finance
- Stock: Reliance Industries
- Data Range: 2017 - 2024

## Features Used
- Previous day prices (lag features)
- Moving averages (5-day, 10-day)
- RSI (Relative Strength Index)

## Model
- Random Forest Regressor

## Evaluation
- RMSE (Root Mean Squared Error)

## Observations
- Model captures general trend but not exact values
- Market volatility affects prediction accuracy

## Future Improvements
- Use LSTM for better time-series prediction
- Add more technical indicators
